    <p class="pg-sub">Berberine has been called "Nature's Ozempic" and "Nature's Metformin" across social media. But how does a plant alkaloid actually compare to one of the most prescribed drugs in the world? We analyze the clinical evidence, mechanisms, and limitations of both compounds for an honest, evidence-based comparison.</p>
