      <p><strong>Medical Disclaimer:</strong> This article is for <strong>educational and informational purposes only</strong>. It is not medical advice, and it does not recommend using berberine as a substitute for metformin or any prescribed medication. Metformin is an FDA-approved prescription drug that should only be taken under physician supervision. Berberine is a dietary supplement. If you have type 2 diabetes, prediabetes, or any metabolic condition, <strong>consult your physician</strong> before making any changes to your treatment plan.</p>
